org.net4care.testdoubles

Class FakeObjectXDSAndObservationCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.net4care.testdoubles.FakeObjectXDSAndObservationCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObservationCache, XDSRepository

    public class FakeObjectXDSAndObservationCache
extends Object
implements XDSRepository, ObservationCache
    FakeObject implementation of the XDS repository and Observation Cache. Stores all HL7 documents and observations in an in-memory list for much faster but non persistent storage to speed up testing.
    Author:
    Net4Care, Henrik Baerbak Christensen, AU
